Some helper functions for ease of use for ecwam repository https://github.com/ecmwf-ifs/ecwam

They should be copied over to your ecwam repo (apart from the first one)
They should be ran in this order

<!-- setup repo -->
xsetup_repo.sh

<!-- build -->
xbuild.sh

<!-- run -->
xrun.sh

<!-- sweep -->
xsweep.sh

<!-- plot -->
xplot.py